Before the initiation of the course all the required software and packages need to be installed in your laptop. The course require working installation of R and R studio in your preferred operating system. Any difficulties arise during installation can be discussed in the slack channel given in the home page of the website. 

### Installation of R & R studio

We use R programming language for all the downstream analysis of transcriptomics data. A detailed description how to install R & R studio on Windows can be found [here](https://teacherscollege.screenstepslive.com/a/1108074-install-r-and-rstudio-for-windows)

